-- Cantor Adds Jefferies’s Rowe, Schlittler at Debt Capital Markets
-- B y   L a u r a   M a r c i n e k
-- 2012-09-11T15:33:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-11/cantor-adds-jefferies-s-rowe-schlittler-at-debt-capital-markets.html
Cantor Fitzgerald LP, the
investment bank planning to add 800 people in coming years,
hired Michael Rowe and Luiz Schlittler as managing directors in
the debt capital markets’ emerging-markets group.  Rowe will focus on emerging-markets corporate bond trading
and Schlittler will work on emerging markets sales, New York-
based Cantor said today in a statement. They were both
previously senior vice presidents at Jefferies Group Inc.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Laura Marcinek in  New York  at 
